chart.name: % of total errors by function
chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.errors', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('azure.function.errors', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum(by=['azure_function_name', 'azure_resource_name', 'azure_region']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B/A).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.description: % of Invocations erred over last 1 minute
chart.name: Error Percentage
chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.errors', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=2).sum(over='1m').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('azure.function.invocations', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='last_value', maxExtrapolations=2).sum(over='1m').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.name: Bytes Sent

chart.name: Bytes Sent vs 24hr Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('BytesSent', filter=filter('primary_aggregation_type', 'true') and filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true')).sum().scale(60).publish(label='A')
B = (A).mean(over='1h').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (B).timeshift('1d').publish(label='C', enable=False)

chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.duration', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('azure.function.invocations', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1m').sum().publish(label='B', enable=False)

chart.name: Invocation Duration
chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.duration', filter=filter('is_Azure_Function', 'true'), rollup='average').mean(by=['azure_function_name', 'azure_resource_name', 'azure_region']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Duration
chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.duration', rollup='average').mean().publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).max().publish(label='B')
C = (A).min().publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='E')
F = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='F')

chart.name: Duration 1d % change for slowest 5
chart.programText:
A = data('azure.function.duration', rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1d').sum(by=['azure_function_name', 'azure_resource_name']).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = data('azure.function.invocations', rollup='sum', extrapolation='zero').sum(over='1d').sum(by=['azure_function_name', 'azure_resource_name']).publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B).top(by=['azure_function_name', 'azure_resource_name'], count=5).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (C).timeshift('1d').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (C/D - 1).scale(100).publish(label='E')
